                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010916-34-off168 t18010916-34-cd169"></join>, a silver table-spoon, value 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010916-34-victim239" type="victimName">
